    "This visual representation can give further insights into precision, recall, and F1-score metrics, contributing to a holistic understanding of the models disease classification capabilities.ANOVA (Analysis of Variance) was conducted to assess the statistical differences in the disease classification performance among four models-Bi-LSTM, CNN, CNN-LSTM, and LSTM-utilized on the KIMORE dataset.",
